==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pyrogen
<hw>Pyr"o*gen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Pyrogenous</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Electricity.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld> <def>A poison separable from
decomposed meat infusions, and supposed to be formed from albuminous
matter through the agency of bacteria.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pyrogenic</ent>⟦br⟧
